channel.title: 508/525 A magical force stops you from teleporting
channel.description:
i've been coding my server for a little over a week now, ive added many things from its blank base i started with. i've added safe zones ( i think i have added correctly) i cannot attack players in these zones, but it does not allow me to use my ::home command, or even normal teles i just get the message "A magical force stops you from teleporting" and i cant understand why, could someone help me please. ive added the places for minigames, e.g jad and once beaten theres no way out, unless i teleport the players to me, which i cant be doing every second. so please could someone help.
lol thanks for nothing -.-
